title: Anjaana
subTitle: Raju, a garage mechanic, falls in love with Rachna but her guardian, Diwan, opposes the marriage and humiliates Raju's mother. Raju decides to exact his revenge against Diwan and teach him a lesson.

title: Teri Maang Sitaron Se Bhar Doon
subTitle: Kamini pretends to be wealthy in front of her daughter, while living a contradictory reality. However, her life takes a surprising turn when her boss, an outlaw named Sultanbhai, comes to her rescue.

title: Baabul
subTitle: After his son's death, Balraj attempts to convince his daughter-in-law Malvika to marry Rajat, her childhood friend. However, his endeavours are disregarded by his wife and elder brother.

title: Do Jasoos
subTitle: Two bumbling detectives, Dharamchand and Karamchand, are assigned to locate a multi-millionaire's daughter, who goes missing after she witnesses a murder.

title: Gautam Govinda
subTitle: Gautam, a dedicated officer, is transferred to a town that is teeming with criminals and ruled by Dharamdutt. In order to tackle Gautam, Dharamdutt sends his most able and trusted man, Govinda.

title: Dushman
subTitle: Surjit Singh, a truck driver, kills a man while driving in the thick fog. However, his life changes when the judge sentences him to serve the victim's family.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Seema, the daughter of a wealthy businessman, falls in love with a labourer. However, complications arise when Seema's father refuses to accept their relationship.

title: Apna Desh
subTitle: Akash, an honest man, loses his job due to the corruption of his seniors. As he strives to get his job back and his brother is wrongly framed, he attempts to fight and prove his brother's innocence.

title: Indrajeet
subTitle: Indrajeet, a retired police officer, sets out to take revenge on his ex-lover's brother and friends for murdering his adopted daughter and son-in-law.

title: Indrajeet
subTitle: Indrajeet, a retired police officer, sets out to take revenge on his ex-lover's brother and friends for murdering his adopted daughter and son-in-law.

title: Rakta Bandhan
subTitle: Chandan is found dead by his twin brother Trishul, who is a dacoit. In a bid to turn a new leaf and leave the criminal life behind, Trishul assumes his brother's identity.

title: Baat Ban Jaye
subTitle: Nisha, a wealthy woman in charge of her family business, does not want to marry a rich man. She falls in love with Suraj Singh, a wedding singer and dancer, without realising that he has other plans.

title: Khel Mohabbat Ka
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Pyari Behna
subTitle: Kaali blames Vinay, an engineer, for an accident in which the former loses his left arm. When Vinay falls in love with Kaali's sister, Seeta, Kaali does not allow him to marry her.

title: Parichay
subTitle: Desperate for work, Ravi takes up the challenge of teaching five spoilt children who have driven away all previous tutors. However, they soon bond and Ravi falls for Rama, the eldest of the lot.

title: Gunga Jumna
subTitle: Ganga perseveres in the village to make his brother a policeman in the city. However, circumstances cause Ganga to become a bandit while Jumna is compelled to convict him.

title: Kohram
subTitle: When a teacher is killed by two village tyrants, Thakur and Kalia, his brother Arjun swears to avenge him. Years later, Arjun kills Thakur and then joins forces with his brother's sons to face Kalia.

title: Ajay
subTitle: Manorama falls in love with Ajay, even though they come from different social backgrounds. They want to get married, but Manorama's uncles try their best to separate the happy couple.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Aakhri Daao
subTitle: Ravi, a burglar, leaves his life of crime behind and starts afresh winning the trust and respect of the local community. His life takes a turn when his former crime partner approaches him with a job.

title: Madhosh
subTitle: Young Raya and Soni fall deeply in love and secretly marry against their families' wishes. However, as time passes, Raya begins to struggle with the challenges of life and starts mistreating Soni.

title: Parivar
subTitle: Gopal and Meena's happy family with their children falls apart when their daughter, Sapna, ends her life and Gopal gets arrested for the murder of Diwanchand, who is responsible for Sapna's distress.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Kuchhe Dhaage
subTitle: To avenge his father's death, Lakhan kills Roopa's father, Tulsiram, in cold blood. Enraged, Roopa decides to kill him, but fate has its own plans.

title: Aage Ki Soch
subTitle: Ganpat, an honest merchant, falls in love with Sapna when she visits his village with her friends. One day, she returns as a married woman, breaking Ganpat's heart.
